{"tid":233660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人分享下被狗追既經驗","createTime":"2017-05-07T16:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T11:34:40.000Z","uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7718572ad77a3c0bb2268b6c052801e83b0de950","tid":233660,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"點避<br />\n有冇咬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30ab19de11aa3c0a4c61772d7b0e83b5641bc5b","tid":233660,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n追番佢轉頭<br />\n然後就會不斷 dumdum轉菊花園"},{"pid":"d21fd2d778657907e7f760595f5d7d8997b6c4d7","tid":233660,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T17:33:24.000Z","msg":"細個住村屋附近<br />\n啲人好鍾意養好多大狗看門口<br />\n咁個時唔知訂 係咁揼地嚇啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知成堆狗望過嚟吠我<br />\n嚇到瀨屎即刻跑走<br />\n成堆狗 講緊10幾隻 狗衝埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心驚膽顫咁向前逃走<br />\n跑跑下著住拖鞋嘅我甩咗隻拖鞋之後成個人仆咗係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫我以為實死無生嘅時候好彩有大人經過幫我趕走啲狗 <br />\n事後我成身損哂俾屋企人話到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起都覺得自己好on9"},{"pid":"981fea7f9dda37c99df6cd12c77dc100e5664d6f","tid":233660,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}